OL,3,CGazan boy's uncontrollable shrieks
OL,4,Cecho during ITV News' chilling
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FITV News Global Security Editor Rohit
OL,8,FKachroo reunites with critically
OL,9,Funwell Abdullah, who was evacuated
OL,10,Ffrom Gaza to Qatar
OL,12,FWe hear Abdullah a few moments before
OL,13,Fwe see him.
OL,15,FHis distant screams are echoing down
OL,16,Fthe corridor at the Turkish hospital
OL,17,Fin downtown . "I am in pain" he
OL,18,Fshouts, in Arabic from afar. "I need
OL,19,Fpainkillers."
