OL,4,Cecho during ITV News' chilling
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FWe travelled with him to Qatar from
OL,8,FEgypt's border with four days earlier.
OL,10,FNow, we are here at the clinic to find
OL,11,Fout what happened to the burned and
OL,12,Fbandaged boy with injuries so severe
OL,13,Fhe was rushed off the military
OL,14,Fevacuation flight, before dozens of
OL,15,Fother wounded passengers.
OL,17,FAs we approach his private room, the
OL,18,Fsound of his yells become louder and
OL,19,Feven more chilling.
