OL,3,CGazan boy's uncontrollable shrieks
OL,4,Cecho during ITV News' chilling
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FA nurse opens the door to reveal the
OL,8,Fsmall frame of the boy behind the
OL,9,Funcontrollable shrieks. Abdullah is
OL,10,Fjust 13 years old.
OL,12,FCasts conceal his badly burned hands,
OL,13,Falthough some of the bandages have
OL,14,Fbeen removed from his head since we
OL,15,Flast saw him.
OL,17,FThey reveal his severe facial scars -
OL,18,Finjuries sustained in an Israeli
OL,19,Fairstrike in Gaza City on December 4.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/9
