OL,3,CGazan boy's uncontrollable shrieks
OL,4,Cecho during ITV News' chilling
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FBut there is much more to his
OL,8,Fagonising screams than his physical
OL,9,Finjuries alone. "I need my father, I
OL,10,Fhave no one else left," he shouts into
OL,11,Fthe air. "I fear for him in this war,
OL,12,Fthat they might bomb him."
OL,14,FAbdullah is not only wounded but
OL,15,Ftraumatised - his mother, sister and
OL,16,Fbrother were killed in that same
OL,17,Fattack.
