OL,4,Cecho during ITV News' chilling
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FHe is in a new country without his
OL,8,Fbeloved father, who survived and is
OL,9,Fstill in Gaza, and can send only
OL,10,Firregular messages because of the poor
OL,11,Fstate of the phone network.
OL,13,FBetween the occasional sound of
OL,14,Fmessage alerts on Abdullah's phone,
OL,15,Fare the periods of silence which can
OL,16,Flast several days, when he is left to
OL,17,Fwonder whether his dad is dead or
OL,18,Falive, safe or in peril.
