OL,3,CGazan boy's uncontrollable shrieks
OL,4,Cecho during ITV News' chilling
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,F"I need my father here with me. I need
OL,8,Fmy father here with me, I can't lose
OL,9,Fhim after I lost everyone else. Oh
OL,10,FGod," he says.
OL,12,FBut Abdullah is not alone. His aunt is
OL,13,Fin the room. She held his hand as they
OL,14,Fflew on the Qatari flight on Sunday,
OL,15,Fbut she knows she cannot fill the gap
OL,16,Fleft by his long lost father.
OL,18,FShe has tried to conceal from him the
OL,19,Fdepths of his own tragedy, but there's
OL,20,Fno hiding it.
