OL,4,Cecho during ITV News' chilling
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,F"The family was trying to flee Gaza"
OL,8,Fshe says, referring to the December
OL,9,Fattack. "They were told to leave west
OL,10,FGaza to go to the east, and then from
OL,11,Fthe east to the west. And then, they
OL,12,Ftargeted them."
OL,14,F"There is no safety at all. People
OL,15,Faren't safe in their houses, and most
OL,16,Fcivilians have nothing to do with this
OL,17,Fwar."
