OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FHer son, Zain, is also in the room,
OL,8,Fsitting for short periods with his
OL,9,Fhead in his hands, before getting up
OL,10,Fto try to help.
OL,12,FHe recognises the importance of his
OL,13,Fnew role, supporting Abdullah, his
OL,14,Folder cousin, as well as his mother.
OL,16,FThe weight of responsibility is
OL,17,Fobvious as, years before adolescence,
OL,18,Fhe takes on the role of father of this
OL,19,Ffamily.
